which matches the action of `Set.mulActionSet`.

These are all available in the `Pointwise` locale.

Additionally, it provides various degrees of monoid structure:
* `AddSubmonoid.one`
* `AddSubmonoid.mul`
* `AddSubmonoid.mulOneClass`
* `AddSubmonoid.semigroup`
